{"tid":1277854,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝一個遊戲app 我學生話警察係...","createTime":"2019-07-02T09:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:36:23.000Z","uid":27131,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dee93ff7dcc8191663cd008f6ef41d7bd3189e03","tid":1277854,"uid":27131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"多謝個遊戲 我學生已成功被洗腦<br />\n佢只得8歲 但係係個沉迷打機者<br />\n休息時間走埋黎同我講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟<br />\n學生：老師你睇下呢個遊戲<br />\n小弟：做咩<br />\n學生：啲警察係壞人黎 殺曬啲人 專恰小朋友呀<br />\n小弟忍唔住笑左笑<br />\n學生：真係架 警察唔係好人佢地壞人黎架 我唔鐘意警察<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢到 小弟深感遊戲既偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟只係想分享趣事一則<br />\n唔好推 想留返啲有用既資訊係熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1a05b936a574c14a0896e7ebd36e733d674ec8","tid":1277854,"uid":70487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"遊戲係文宣嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96bfe77cbce737035995f796dc75398afa933e5","tid":1277854,"uid":27131,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4d1a05b936a574c14a0896e7ebd36e733d674ec8","tid":1277854,"uid":70487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"遊戲係文宣嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"真 我都比佢既偉論嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b242a1b752434016cc218ae396bfe905cfbadee3","tid":1277854,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"如果太直接既話 可以話隻驚入面d警察中晒喪屍毒比人控制左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533e65c23a3d900084a0f3de335814d806e7a804","tid":1277854,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打整㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5d5a75bc01535e565237853c1f7d52cc91f89a","tid":1277854,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b242a1b752434016cc218ae396bfe905cfbadee3","tid":1277854,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"如果太直接既話 可以話隻驚入面d警察中晒喪屍毒比人控制左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"中左非洲變種豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f81aa78abd1c4357f20989d249e9aad1c241eb","tid":1277854,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"咩驚,link呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c343af56c3ec572eebed62332fac001d97dadfd","tid":1277854,"uid":188969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"文宣既戰爭開始！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"667ba8e1068fd40030603881e1e0df348c009be2","tid":1277854,"uid":256899,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"好心唔好用洗腦 一陣又比人CAP出黎-"},{"pid":"2461e19cc3c0c1fcd329c2ee9c7a3b7043cce356","tid":1277854,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"咩GAME"},{"pid":"c71c374f9aa088df1915f8c29866179f2d8e6561","tid":1277854,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:28:00.000Z","msg":"建議你喺時事台再出po，同開game名，因為呢個做法真係有創意同有用，要推上去俾人知。文宣又可以做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你見還願被中共封殺就知道中共幾驚遊戲宣傳反共思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好推到有人真係整遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人肯做，發動埋全港眾籌幫手仲得，整多幾隻game都得，整埋多語言版本更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲內容同形式可以多元化。內容可以包括反送中示威遊行，高官有幾無恥，黑警有幾變態，tvb有幾偏頗，中共有咩手段，遊行示威者有幾勇敢同守秩序，抗爭手法幾有創意同deep learning。<br />\n<br />\n形式無拘，選項式視覺小說，RPG，動作遊戲（示威者vs黑警），可以盡情發揮創意。<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔介意，我都想用呢個idea出po，我可以解釋得詳細一啲"},{"pid":"fb4a029e0c60f0fd5300f7f626895a43ec898955","tid":1277854,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:33:17.000Z","msg":"例子：Va11-Hall（視覺小說）<br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/447530/header.jpg?t=1517266908\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F447530%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1517266908&h=903727e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網評轉載：<br />\n雖然 Va11-Hall A的背景是賽博朋克的未來世界，故事的不少內容，其實是映射委內瑞拉的國內動盪。委內瑞拉是遊戲製作人的出生地，發生的動盪和香港的不同，內容卻很應景：<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n由於持續不斷的經濟與安全危機，城中已經爆發過無數次抗議，Glitch City的總理quincy對此明確表示：如果暴徒再奪走一位市民的生命，他就要親自動筆寫下新的法令，禁止一切公開示威<br />\n<br />\n「這種事情不能再繼續下去了，」quincy通過電話對AE表示。「他們只想毀掉公共財產。那些傢伙積極地破壞我們為恢復這座美麗城市說做出的努力。我們已經決定了：如果他們額度行為再導致一個市民傷亡，我就會盡我所能禁止一切抗議活動，屆時白騎士將被授權動用極端武力。<br />\n//"},{"pid":"3367b8e337b03e94751151fc456a470736eefcc3","tid":1277854,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:41:24.000Z","msg":"咩game?"},{"pid":"3a8563df6757bca74dd4a5ed27d2b36d6a37ba4e","tid":1277854,"uid":159913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T20:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJXBd3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJXBd3U.jpg&h=3d145eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察有一半時間都係仆街嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfe5aeecf350f539150917e25057fd0d8cb2a5b","tid":1277854,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同中共同一個做法"}]}